        "template": "<div style=\"background-color: #1e1e2e; border: 1px solid #313244; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\">\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #cdd6f4;\">ML Busy Status Prediction</h4>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n    <span style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1em; color: {{#payload.prediction}} {{.}} {{/payload.prediction}} === 'BUSY' ? '#f38ba8' : '#a6e3a1';\">\n      {{payload.prediction}}\n    </span>\n    <span style=\"background-color: #89b4fa; color: #11111b; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: bold;\">\n      {{payload.confidence}} Confidence\n    </span>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-top: 8px; font-size: 0.75em; color: #a6adc8;\">\n    Predicted Hour: {{payload.predicted_hour}}:00<br/>\n    Features: {{payload.features_used.day_of_week}}, Hour {{payload.features_used.hour}}\n  </div>\n</div>",
